cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a secure inference framework based on homomorphic encryption and secret sharing for privacy-preserving visual recognition. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper focuses on visual recognition tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the accuracy-efficiency trade-offs in the context of machine learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is possible as the paper proposes a framework for efficient execution of secure inference. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with visual recognition tasks and secure inference in the context of multimedia data.
